/blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日都想早啲訓，一邊諗一邊都係打字覆post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f240c5c98718e9f475411c6778a58a5049bbffd","tid":9664,"uid":10724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>皮膚開始差，以前玩通宵第二日仲好正常，呢家晏訓啲第二日已經攰到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁 其實我好憎通頂 次次搞到自己好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日都想早啲訓，一邊諗一邊都係打字覆post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時唔係唔想訓 而係太多野諗搞到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902b63607a0ea302a5253cf2d9fc147db1483fad","tid":9664,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>90後係度話自己老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同bb比實老咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我仲諗住入黎認真偈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打幾歲 冇計 可能我份人睇野比較遠 所以覺得自己老</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n29， 真正覺得唔再年輕，唔再係18 22。體力不再，返輪班通頂攰到仆街。本身夜瞓咗好多年，身體差咗好多。我個人思想比較老績，心境好似40歲咁。加上啱啱經歷咗兩段刻骨銘心既愛情，成為遺憾，仲傷心難過緊，感覺又再老多幾年。<br />\n<br />\n年輕不再<br />\n<br />\n珍惜年輕既身體同心境吖90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}